1
00:00:10,506 --> 00:00:13,570
The body found at the crime scene belonged to Enforcer Yamatoya from Division 2.

2
00:00:14,531 --> 00:00:16,542
The enforcement was carried out with a Dominator,

3
00:00:16,542 --> 00:00:19,583
and the shooter was Division 2's own Inspector Shisui.

4
00:00:20,546 --> 00:00:25,559
After carrying out the enforcement, she absconded with Yamatoya's Dominator and hasn't been seen since.

5
00:00:25,559 --> 00:00:27,559
So an Inspector went missing...

6
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:31,506
Frankly, I don't know what to make of this.

7
00:00:31,506 --> 00:00:33,550
We don't have much else to go on for now.

8
00:00:45,533 --> 00:00:46,599
WC?

9
00:00:46,599 --> 00:00:47,503

10
00:01:05,076 --> 00:01:08,071
I will go insane

11
00:01:03,571 --> 00:01:06,505
if the world keeps ruining my life

12
00:01:07,546 --> 00:01:10,555
I've stopped breathing

13
00:01:10,555 --> 00:01:13,514
from the nervousness every day

14
00:01:13,514 --> 00:01:15,505
Enigmatic feeling

15
00:01:20,598 --> 00:01:23,598
I have to be the aggressor

16
00:01:23,598 --> 00:01:26,565
The world has stopped making sense

17
00:01:26,507 --> 00:01:28,553
It's dissolving

18
00:01:27,598 --> 00:01:30,565
God has come to us

19
00:01:30,565 --> 00:01:33,507
with sword in hand

20
00:01:34,553 --> 00:01:37,591
The world has split in two

21
00:01:37,591 --> 00:01:39,570
Half is mad,

22
00:01:39,570 --> 00:01:41,571
and so am I

23
00:01:41,571 --> 00:01:43,537
Where's the difference?

24
00:01:43,537 --> 00:01:44,596
Where's the difference?

25
00:01:44,596 --> 00:01:48,521
Only God can walk the borderline

26
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:51,588
I'm going crazy, I'm going crazy

27
00:01:51,588 --> 00:01:55,543
Will I find you killed by my own hand?

28
00:01:54,593 --> 00:01:58,564
Crazy, crazy, floating on the water

29
00:01:58,564 --> 00:02:01,581
I have no focus in my soul

30
00:02:01,585 --> 00:02:05,548
Shake me, shake me, floating on the water

31
00:02:05,548 --> 00:02:08,552
I can't even look into the mirror

32
00:02:16,595 --> 00:02:17,508
the creeping unknown

33
